{"tid":770953,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)烈探狙擊 惡靈戰警 皇家特工1-2","createTime":"2018-08-07T13:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T20:31:34.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"61a722abc044cfc288e2ef0791b588153ae9ed94","tid":770953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:36:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=60D7r1Bpq9sz4tlH9ThaNywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c7a7ab24\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=60D7r1Bpq9sz4tlH9ThaNywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=5198e6bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=60D7r1Bpq9sz4tlH9ThaNywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=3ca3fd20\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d1/Jack_Reacher_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd1%2FJack_Reacher_poster.jpg&h=effc1eaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/ea/Ghost_Rider.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fea%2FGhost_Rider.jpg&h=8009b454&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/8b/Kingsman_The_Secret_Service_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F8b%2FKingsman_The_Secret_Service_poster.jpg&h=fd1bb461&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/4/42/Kingsman_The_Golden_Circle_Poster.jpg/220px-Kingsman_The_Golden_Circle_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F4%2F42%2FKingsman_The_Golden_Circle_Poster.jpg%2F220px-Kingsman_The_Golden_Circle_Poster.jpg&h=3adf5e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一個尋常的小鎮，一如往常的早晨，五個人照常過日子，卻慘遭隨機射殺。所有證據都指向一個人：槍法神準的殺手，他前身是軍人，訓練有素的狙擊兵。他很快就遭到逮捕與拘提。經過漫長的訊問，依然問不出什麼。囚犯只做出一個神祕的要求，隨手寫下：「給我Jack Reacher」。誰是Jack？這問題令人費解..<br />\n<br />\n2.火爆強尼(尼古拉斯&middot;凱奇 飾)原本是一個摩托車特技演員，為了拯救他父親的生命，他將自己的靈魂出賣給惡魔梅菲斯特(彼得&middot;方達 飾)，然而邪惡的勢力竟讓他走火入魔，化身為被詛咒的惡靈戰警，所到之處都引燃熊熊烈焰。而強尼漸漸開始學習控制自己的能力，將無法抑制的憤怒發洩在為非作歹的歹徒身上。但他情不自禁愛上了一個追逐他新聞的女記者(伊娃&middot;曼德絲 飾)，卻因失去靈魂飽受痛楚折磨；而他又將如何對抗更大的惡魔勢力呢?<br />\n<br />\n3.「金士曼」表面上是英國倫敦薩佛街上的一家裁縫店，天天為客戶量身打造帥氣的西服，實際上卻是一個歷史淵源久遠的民間諜報組織，以世界和平為宗旨，曾經多次打擊了嚴重犯罪，卻極為低調，不欲人知。但他們的能力卻不亞於英國秘密情報局（俗稱軍情六處，MI6）、美國中央情報局（CIA）、俄國對外情報局（FIS，原為KGB第一總局）、以色列情報特務局（MOSSAD）等知名的國家情治單位，<br />\n1997年「金士曼」的一群探員潛入位於中東的恐怖組織巢穴，順利逮捕其首腦，特務哈利&middot;哈特（代號加拉哈德，取自英國傳奇《圓桌武士》）審問首腦時，卻因一時失誤沒發現首腦想用手榴彈同歸於盡，導致一名探員用肉身阻擋而英勇犧牲，雖然救了其他人，但也讓哈特感到十分愧疚......<br />\n<br />\n4.一年前，伊格西&middot;安文率間諜組織「金士曼特務」挫敗里奇蒙&middot;范倫坦播送神經波廣播毀滅全人類的陰謀後，拿下師父哈利&middot;哈特的代號－「加拉哈德」，和瑞典皇室的提兒蒂公主在一起生活。一次回家路上，在瓦倫丁事件中丟掉手臂和聲帶的金士曼特務落選者查理&middot;赫斯基伏擊了伊格西。伊格西在倫敦的飆車大戰中躲避查理與他一眾手下的追殺，但查理切斷他的機械手臂，利用車子的電腦系統駭入金士曼的伺服器。伊格西出席瑞典皇室晚宴期間，金士曼的總部和所有特務（除了梅林外）的住宅都被飛彈摧毀，英國所有金士曼特務都被除掉<br />\n<br />\n9 45PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=60D7r1Bpq9sz4tlH9ThaNywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=2276e628\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=60D7r1Bpq9sz4tlH9ThaNywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=944f9c95\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bae007ec36a7398e1695fe1c5e721ed9a338b04","tid":770953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9cd63852e3a7c7fc60895bfbffd71e87599497","tid":770953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bf9f24c238575e29b3acc8dc9a1ddc8f1e542b","tid":770953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T14:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e58f2eda24e532b0107f8a805bb368ef4a12f9","tid":770953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T15:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab11c65ba0953271513b2498eddc3f8ded0e9143"